data.description: Welcome home to 3810 Altino Court! This waterfront property has 5 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, game room, media room, formal dining room, breakfast nook, study/office and covered patio. Home also has a 220volt plug installed in garage for rapid EV charging! The home is a waterfront that has straight access to the water! The home offers amazing entertaining space with an open floor plan. Come own a piece of comfort, style and luxury before it's too late.
